1
00:00:42,040 --> 00:00:42,440
Come.

2
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:45,610
You're back.

3
00:00:49,560 --> 00:00:49,890
Come.

4
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:51,000
Put your bag down.

5
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:52,600
Baby.

6
00:00:53,360 --> 00:00:54,200
Are you hungry?

7
00:00:54,200 --> 00:00:55,080
What do you want to eat?

8
00:00:55,080 --> 00:00:56,410
Mom will cook it for you.

9
00:00:58,400 --> 00:00:58,880
Dandan,

10
00:00:59,080 --> 00:00:59,880
you must be tired.

11
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:01,280
Do you want to rest a bit first?

12
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:01,720
Dad,

13
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:02,720
I'm not tired.

14
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:04,040
Mom,

15
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:06,400
I want to eat your salt and pepper spare ribs.

16
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:08,200
I haven't had them in a long time.

17
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:09,820
Mom will go prepare it now.

18
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:11,039
Dawei,

19
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:13,020
go buy some spare ribs now.

20
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:14,120
And while you're at it,

21
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:15,800
buy some more of Dandan's favorite food.

22
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:16,360
Okay.

23
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:17,280
Dandan,

24
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:18,000
Dad

25
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,200
is going to buy it for you right now.

26
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:21,000
It's definitely your favorite.

27
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,060
Wait for me.

28
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:49,920
Looking at those fields outside every day in the past,

29
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:52,560
I never thought there was anything nice about them.

30
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,960
Now I understand.

31
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:55,960
Some things,

32
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,740
even if they are ordinary,

33
00:01:58,160 --> 00:02:00,360
are not something everyone can have.

34
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:14,140
My favorite thing to do in the past

35
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,920
was sitting on you

36
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:18,820
and watching the sunset outside the window.

37
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:19,760
Old friend,

38
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,600
long time no see.

39
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:34,530
Here.

40
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:34,960
Eat.

41
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:36,160
Dad,

42
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:36,800
Mom.

43
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:37,920
Haven't we

44
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,720
taken a picture together for a long time?

45
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:41,050
Today's meal is so rich.

46
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,440
Why don't we take a family portrait,

47
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:43,240
a group photo?

48
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:44,400
Okay.

49
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,480
Three.

50
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,600
Cheese.

51
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:55,920
One more.

52
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:03,490
Okay.

53
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:04,200
Let's eat.

54
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,120
Dandan,

55
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:10,800
eat up.

56
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:15,280
These are the salt and pepper ribs you've been talking about.

57
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:15,920
Eat more.

58
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,079
Mom,

59
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,840
these ribs are really delicious.

60
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,040
You are the best cook.

61
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,000
Little foodie.

62
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:30,200
Eat more.

63
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:36,600
Dad,

64
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,400
you've worked hard cooking and washing vegetables.

65
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,530
Let me do the dishes.

66
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,200
You shouldn't wash the dishes.

67
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,600
You just got out of the hospital.

68
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:43,640
Don't be so clumsy.

69
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:44,900
Don't break the bowls.

70
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,240
Dandan,

71
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:48,560
come have some fruit.

72
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,800
Let your dad do the dishes.

73
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,760
He has nothing else to do anyway.

74
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:51,440
Listen to your mother.

75
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:51,770
Go on.

76
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:53,240
I'll go wash my hands first.

77
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:53,570
Okay.

78
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:14,720
Mom,

79
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:16,160
the weather is nice outside.

80
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,360
Let's go get some sun.

81
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:18,839
Okay.

82
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:19,640
Okay.

83
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:20,440
Let's go.

84
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:23,450
Let's go.

85
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:01,600
Dad,

86
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,000
Mom.

87
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,320
I'm leaving.

88
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,520
Don't be sad.

89
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,960
I just went to another world.

90
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,480
In that world,

91
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,640
I have a new life.

92
00:05:19,280 --> 00:05:20,960
I made a lot of new friends.

93
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,210
They are all very good to me.

94
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:24,640
Even,

95
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,840
I have someone I like.

96
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,040
Don't worry.

97
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,120
Even in another world,

98
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:37,040
I will miss you.

99
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:38,200
Dandan.

100
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,440
So,

101
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,120
you must live well.

102
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:47,680
Dandan.

103
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:51,080
Take good care of yourselves.

104
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,360
Dandan.

105
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,320
Dandan.

106
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:18,000
Welcome back,

107
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:18,760
Lu Danyu.

108
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:21,680
Yiyi,

109
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,180
you're still here.

110
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,720
That's great.

111
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,280
I'm so glad to see you again.

112
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:28,080
Yiyi.

113
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,080
I'm also very glad

114
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:31,810
that you can stay in this world.

115
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:37,400
I seem to feel some

116
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,120
very

117
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:40,080
subtle feeling.

118
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,520
This world

119
00:06:41,960 --> 00:06:42,440
seems to

120
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,560
like me a lot.

121
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:44,280
Yes.

122
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:45,560
Because of you,

123
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,690
the world was saved.

124
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:47,760
So the whole world

125
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:49,290
is welcoming your arrival.

126
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:50,800
So

127
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:53,360
the feeling of being paid attention to by the world

128
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,440
is like this.

129
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:56,280
Then,

130
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:58,760
do the Children of the World

131
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,640
also feel the same way?

132
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,840
You are more special than them.

133
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,170
But if you understand it

134
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,620
that way, it works too.

135
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:07,720
By the way,

136
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,100
where is Ayuan?

137
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,820
Still at Fengling Stream.

138
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,370
By the way, Xiaoxue,

139
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:18,240
did you like

140
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,520
the elixirs I gave you

141
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:20,680
last time?

142
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:21,960
Yes,

143
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,120
of course.

144
00:07:25,080 --> 00:07:26,610
Who wouldn't like elixirs?

145
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:28,300
From now on,

146
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,120
I

147
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:29,760
will gather

148
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:30,720
lots and lots of elixirs for you.

149
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,580
How about that?

150
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,080
Okay.

151
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:33,680
But

152
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,440
will the elixirs you gather

153
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,680
be just for me alone?

154
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:38,400
Of course.

155
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,480
As long as you like them,

156
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,880
I'll give them all to you.

157
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:43,520
Then,

158
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,320
Xiaoxue,

159
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:46,159
if you agree,

160
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:48,040
after the hot summer season,

161
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:48,760
I'll ask my father

162
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:49,960
to propose marriage.

163
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,040
What do you think?

164
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,400
Brother Wuzhou,

165
00:07:58,400 --> 00:07:59,480
Sister Mu,

166
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:01,010
what are you talking about?

167
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,320
We didn't say anything.

168
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,080
I see.

169
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,200
Danyu,

170
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,680
didn't you go out for training?

171
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,840
Why are you still here?

172
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:12,320
Yeah.

173
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:15,080
A-Yuan and I

174
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:16,120
discussed it.

175
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,200
Then,

176
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:18,560
we will go together.

177
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:20,680
It's better to go together,

178
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:23,140
so I won't worry about your safety out there.

179
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,940
Alright, Brother Wuzhou.

180
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,200
Stop nagging.

181
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,760
I'm leaving now.

182
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:31,280
You two can talk about your marriage.

183
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,440
I won't disturb you.

184
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,159
I'm off.

185
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:33,799
Bye.

186
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:35,679
So,

187
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,460
she heard everything.

188
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:41,049
It's all your fault.

189
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,520
A-Yuan.

190
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:23,240
I am back.

191
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,080
A-Yuan.

192
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:35,240
Five years later.

193
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:37,060
It has been five years.

194
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:39,660
I didn't expect to be able to come back again.

195
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:41,120
I thought the world consciousness

196
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,880
would be hard to recover in a short time.

197
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:45,010
I didn't expect to return here so soon.

198
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:47,560
Great.

199
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,640
Dad, Mom,

200
00:09:48,920 --> 00:09:50,280
I can see you again.
